<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 01:27:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国宇航局漫游者在火星上发现了稀有有机分子</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/nasa-rover-uncovers-rare-organic-molecules-on-mars</link><description>“我们认为我们正在研究在火星上保存了 35 亿年的有机物质，”艾米·威廉姆斯博士说。 [ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nasa-rover-uncovers-rare-organic-molecules-on-mars.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 01:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/nasa-rover-uncovers-rare-organic-molecules-on-mars</guid></item><item><title>宇航员如何在零重力下重新学习握力控制</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/how-astronauts-relearn-grip-control-in-zero-gravity</link><description>太空旅行如何影响宇航员的大脑和身体反应？这是最近发表在 JNeurosci 上的一项研究希望作为一个科学家团队解决的问题 |空间&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-astronauts-relearn-grip-control-in-zero-gravity.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 01:12:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/how-astronauts-relearn-grip-control-in-zero-gravity</guid></item><item><title>紫外线相机捕捉到暴风雨期间树叶上发光的日冕</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/uv-camera-captures-glowing-coronae-on-leaves-during-storms</link><description>帕特里克·麦克法兰说：“肉眼几乎看不见它，但我们的仪器可以看到当雷暴从头顶掠过时，大片闪烁的日冕在发光。” [ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/uv-camera-captures-glowing-coronae-on-leaves-during-storms.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 00:57:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/uv-camera-captures-glowing-coronae-on-leaves-during-storms</guid></item><item><title>雪转雨 美国西部供水面临风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/western-u-s-water-supply-at-risk-as-snow-turns-to-rain</link><description>扎卡里亚·巴特勒说：“这项研究为改进水资源对气候变化响应的预测迈出了关键一步，并强调了将水传输时间动态纳入未来水文评估的价值。” [ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/western-u-s-water-supply-at-risk-as-snow-turns-to-rain.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 00:42:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/western-u-s-water-supply-at-risk-as-snow-turns-to-rain</guid></item><item><title>MLKL 的自抑制控制控制坏死性凋亡过程中的假激酶结构域磷酸化和寡聚化</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/autoinhibitory-control-of-mlkl-governs-pseudokinase-domain-phosphorylation-and-oligomerization-during-necroptosis</link><description>目前的坏死性凋亡模型假设 MLKL 的 N 末端细胞毒性结构域在 RIPK3 磷酸化的同时从自身抑制中释放出来。 Pan 和 Abbott 表明，抑制 MLKL 的 N 末端可消除 RIPK3 的磷酸化，而去除或解除 N 末端和中间结构域之间的自抑制可促进其磷酸化。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/autoinhibitory-control-of-mlkl-governs-pseudokinase-domain-phosphorylation-and-oligomerization-during-necroptosis2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 00:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/autoinhibitory-control-of-mlkl-governs-pseudokinase-domain-phosphorylation-and-oligomerization-during-necroptosis</guid></item><item><title>支持 GLP1 激动剂药物降低血压与减肥效果无关的概念</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/supporting-the-concept-that-glp1-agonist-drugs-lower-bloodpressure-independent-from-their-weight-loss-effects</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 00:12:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/supporting-the-concept-that-glp1-agonist-drugs-lower-bloodpressure-independent-from-their-weight-loss-effects</guid></item><item><title>糖尿病诱导的 TREM2 内皮细胞信号传导损害缺血性血管修复</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/diabetes-induced-trem2-endothelial-cell-signaling-impairs-ischemic-vascular-repair</link><description>科学家们建立了糖尿病血管图谱，并破译了“泡沫状”吞噬细胞和内皮细胞之间的串扰，表明 TREM2 会导致外周动脉疾病中的血管功能障碍。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/diabetes-induced-trem2-endothelial-cell-signaling-impairs-ischemic-vascular-repair2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 23:57:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/diabetes-induced-trem2-endothelial-cell-signaling-impairs-ischemic-vascular-repair</guid></item><item><title>Tau 蛋白血液检测可在大脑变化前数年检测出阿尔茨海默病风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/tau-blood-test-detects-alzheimers-disease-risk-years-before-brain-changes</link><description>新研究表明，血浆磷酸化 tau 217 (pTau217) 可以在传统 PET 扫描出现之前数年检测出阿尔茨海默病的病理学。在纵向研究中，pTau217 水平升高准确预测了目前无症状的健康老年人未来淀粉样蛋白的积累和认知能力下降。虽然尚未推荐用于常规临床筛查，但该生物标志物提供了一个潜在的“时钟”，用于估计三到四年内症状的发作。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tau-blood-test-detects-alzheimers-disease-risk-years-before-brain-changes.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 23:42:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/tau-blood-test-detects-alzheimers-disease-risk-years-before-brain-changes</guid></item><item><title>OTOF 相关性耳聋的多中心基因治疗随访长达 2.5 年</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/multicentre-gene-therapy-for-otof-related-deafness-followed-up-to-2-5-years</link><description>由麻省总医院和复旦大学眼耳鼻喉科医院的研究人员共同领导的一项新的国际研究表明，针对一种罕见遗传性耳聋的基因疗法成功地恢复了大多数参与者的听力，效果可持续长达 2.5 年。该结果是迄今为止最大规模的遗传性听力损失基因治疗临床试验，也是迄今为止报告的最长的随访结果，发表在&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/multicentre-gene-therapy-for-otof-related-deafness-followed-up-to-2-5-years.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 23:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/multicentre-gene-therapy-for-otof-related-deafness-followed-up-to-2-5-years</guid></item><item><title>新研究揭示了流行减肥药物的隐藏副作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-research-uncovers-hidden-side-effects-of-popular-weight-loss-drugs</link><description>对 Reddit 帖子的人工智能分析发现了 GLP-1 药物可能被低估的潜在副作用，证明了社交媒体在早期药物安全见解中的价值。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-research-uncovers-hidden-side-effects-of-popular-weight-loss-drugs.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 23:12:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-research-uncovers-hidden-side-effects-of-popular-weight-loss-drugs</guid></item></channel></rss>